!! Transforms

A //transform// is a named function that reshapes a token's value before substitution.  The plugin ships a handful of built-ins and lets you add your own.

This guide reuses the [[Usage guide|$:/plugins/crosseye/json-convert/usage]]'s transform chapters so there's one source of truth.  Read them here as a unit, or in context inside the Usage guide.

